### 行动 3（分析阶段）：开始挖掘种子库价值

VACUUM 完成后，用以下方向开始分析（等用户确认分析方向后再执行）：

**推荐分析查询（供参考，不要自行执行）**：
```sql
-- Top 策略（按期望比率排序）
SELECT strategy, AVG(expectancy_ratio), AVG(win_rate), COUNT(*)
FROM combo_summary
GROUP BY strategy
ORDER BY AVG(expectancy_ratio) DESC LIMIT 10;

-- 按 Regime 分组的策略 avg_r
SELECT cs.strategy, pt.regime_at_open, AVG(pt.r_value), COUNT(*)
FROM paired_trades pt JOIN combo_summary cs ON pt.combo_id = cs.id
GROUP BY cs.strategy, pt.regime_at_open
ORDER BY AVG(pt.r_value) DESC;

-- Bull regime 下胜率 > 60% 的 combo
SELECT strategy, coin, interval, win_rate, sharpe_ratio
FROM combo_summary
WHERE win_rate > 60
ORDER BY sharpe_ratio DESC LIMIT 20;
```

